---
title: Honey-Garlic Tossed Chicken with Potato Wedges
description: Let's be honest, we all love sticky sweet sauces on crispy bits of chicken. A dusting of cornstarch and a pop in the oven give chicken thighs a perfectly crisp exterior without all the fuss of deep frying. Ranch dressing and crisp potato wedges round out this meal that pays homage to wing night!
